com.hazelcast.concurrent.idgen

Class IdGeneratorImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hazelcast.concurrent.idgen.IdGeneratorImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DistributedObject, IdGenerator

    public class IdGeneratorImpl
extends Object
implements IdGenerator
    Generates blocks with the help of an IAtomicLong.

    For each block, ID generation is simply a volatile increment.
